data.description: New Year New Price. YOU WON'T WANT TO MISS THIS SPACIOUS & TASTEFULLY UPDATED UNIT TUCKED IN A PARK LIKE SETTING IN THE BEAUTIFULLY MAINTAINED 55+ IMPERIAL PINES COMMUNITY.  SITUATED AMONGST MATURE TREES AND GORGEOUS LANDSCAPING IS THIS 2 BEDROOM, 2 BATHROOM 1145 SQ. FT. UNIT.  THE KITCHEN BOASTS CUSTOM MADE CABINETS WITH LOADS OF STORAGE INCLUDING A SEPARATE PANTRY, Quartz COUNTERTOPS, A DINING SPACE/BREAKFAST NOOK AND PLENTY OF COUNTER SPACE. THE DINING ROOM HAS CUSTOM BUILT IN STORAGE AS WELL. THE PRIMARY BEDROOM HAS SLIDERS THAT OPEN TO A HUGE BALCONY WITH SERENE VIEWS, THE ATTACHED PRIMARY BATH HAS TASTEFUL UPDATES THAT INCLUDE CUSTOM CABINETS WITH MARBLE COUNTERTOPS AND NEWER FIXTURES.  THE LARGE 2ND BEDROOM FEATURES MORE CUSTOM CABINETS FOR ADDITIONAL STORAGE.  VERY OPEN FLOORPLAN FEELS MUCH BIGGER WITH THE FLORIDA ROOM THAT HAS SLIDERS TO THE HUGE BALCONY, (ONLY FIRST FLOOR UNITS HAVE BALCONIES!!) AND OPENS TO THE OUTSIDE. THERE'S INSIDE LAUNDRY WITH ROOM FOR A STACKABLE WASHER & DRYER, HURRICANE SHUTTER FOR THE SLIDERS.  DESIRABLE LOCATION WITH SHOPS & DINING RIGHT ACROSS THE STREET, AND CLOSE PROXIMITY TO COUNTRYSIDE MALL, DOWNTOWN SAFETY HARBOR, LOCAL MEDICAL FACILITIES. EASY ACCESS TO AREA BEACHES & AIRPORTS.  THE COMMUNITY HAS A GATED ENTRY AND SECURE ELEVATOR ACCESS.  THERE'S A POOL, CLUBHOUSE, WALKING TRAILS & PLENTY OF GUEST PARKING.  YOUR FEES INCLUDE EXTERIOR MAINTENANCE, GROUNDS & POOL MAINTENANCE, WATER, SEWER, TRASH & CABLE!
